 with support@elastic.co.\n\nOn account support@elastic.co I can view some interesting apps like Elastic Cloud Admin (QA-Canary) etc ...\n\nI have tried to launch apps and successful authorization this \n\u003ehttps://adminconsole-qa-eu-west-1.aws.qa.cld.elstc.co/deployments\n\nI do not do anything after logged in adminconsole. My IP address is **█████**\n\n{F771084}\n## Steps To Reproduce:\n\n  1. Go to https://staging.found.no/ and Signup an account with email @elastic.co \n  1. Go to https://auth-sandbox.elastic.co and login with email/password you have registered\n{F771085}\n  1. After logged in, you are able to see the apps \n{F771083}\n\n## Impact\n\nWith this vulnerability an attacker was allowed to view apps only visible to employees with email @elastic.co","weakness":{"id":26,"name":"Improper Access Control - Generic"},"original_report_id":null,"original_report_url":null,"attachments":[{"id":771083,"file_name":"auth-sandbox_dashboard.png","expiring_url":"https://hackerone-us-west-2-production-attachments.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/fjyGqyaqpxuwzYbppJzRTJuA?response-content-disposition=attachment%3B%20filename%3D%22auth-sandbox_dashboard.png%22%3B%20filename%2A%3DUTF-8%27%27auth-sandbox_dashboard.png\u0026response-content-type=image%2Fpng\u0026X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256\u0026X-Amz-Credential=ASIAQGK6FURQQGZ6LTSB%2F20260429%2Fus-west-2%2Fs3%2Faws4_request\u0026X-Amz-Date=20260429T083631Z\u0026X-Amz-Expires=3600\u0026X-Amz-Security-Token=IQoJb3JpZ2luX2VjECgaCXVzLXdlc3QtMiJHMEUCIQC7mqe46kPhJeVkT%2BfOYRKXUga5A2lKJha3jedcj2dbrAIgZYk%2BllrT%2FPgvgfWFGwYZfTQUiZvbn1zWZRAPbx5dFQgquwUI8f%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2FARADGgwwMTM2MTkyNzQ4NDkiDIxgP0T6EsSYlHCEAiqPBWnwK3BpWWlBO5SUOYmGLWgtu5CiVqHv04NUQStRYf9idDNWhyUG%2Br1B%2BXVsgn1%2B8meqMDKS0i86vF3ZvHhx8KEghsYuiuTmF2JZQCdzbiaevkFLTyyBT0LlTa2u%2BDzTOoOAIcQ4IO1XRf37kKvkDeZXTp0%2B999jyfZJ38pjnbr4pYpErtV2mBpGeH4plXxxXT2EyIsZjeGYwQXBt5WBgBmJxzDMqWMayu4EUbV75x3b0Jr7f1EyBZgz%2FgFz%2B1C8F7RFxjIhYiIQEe6bDKEz6GzIJNvyhX4jMF9ntXu